<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mortgage Calculator</title>
    <style>
        /* Add some basic styling for clarity */
        .mortgage-form {
            width: 300px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .mortgage-form label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .mortgage-form input[type="text"], .mortgage-form select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .mortgage-form button {
            padding: 10px 15px;
            background-color: #007BFF;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="mortgage-form">
    <form action="submit-form-link-here" method="post">
        <label for="loan-amount">Loan Amount:</label>
        <input type="text" id="loan-amount" name="loanAmount" value="300000">

        <label for="property-value">Property Value:</label>
        <input type="text" id="property-value" name="propertyValue" value="330000">

        <label for="interest-rate">Interest Rate:</label>
        <input type="text" id="interest-rate" name="interestRate" value="5.5">

        <label for="mortgage-term">Mortgage Term:</label>
        <input type="text" id="mortgage-term" name="mortgageTerm" value="30">

        <label for="property-tax">Property Tax:</label>
        <input type="text" id="property-tax" name="propertyTax" value="4950">

        <label for="property-insurance">Property Insurance:</label>
        <input type="text" id="property-insurance" name="propertyInsurance" value="330000">

        <label for="pmi">PMI:</label>
        <input type="text" id="pmi" name="pmi" value="0.52">

        <label for="first-payment-date">First Payment Date:</label>
        <select id="first-payment-date" name="firstPaymentDate">
            <option value="jan">January</option>
            <option value="feb">February</option>
            <option value="mar">March</option>
            <!-- ... Add the rest of the months ... -->
            <option value="sep" selected>September</option>
            <option value="oct">October</option>
            <option value="nov">November</option>
            <option value="dec">December</option>
        </select>
        <input type="text" name="paymentYear" value="2010">

        <button type="submit">Calculate</button>
    </form>
</div>

</body>
</html>
```

Note that the action attribute in the form tag is set to a placeholder value "submit-form-link-here", and you'd need to replace it with the actual URL where the form data should be sent for processing.
